com.microsoft.tfs.core.clients.framework.catalog
Class CatalogNode

java.lang.Object
  com.microsoft.tfs.core.internal.wrappers.WebServiceObjectWrapper
      com.microsoft.tfs.core.clients.framework.catalog.CatalogNode

public class CatalogNode
extends com.microsoft.tfs.core.internal.wrappers.WebServiceObjectWrapper

Wrapper class for the _CatalogNode proxy object of the TFS catalog web service. A CatalogNode represents a node in the catalogs resource hierarchy.

Thread-safety:
thread-safe
Since:
TEE-SDK-10.1
